  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> ginger</strong>, then add to a large bowl with the <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>coconut yoghurt</strong> (save the rest for later!) and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> and give everything a good mix up until the chicken is fully coated in the marinade, then refrigerate until later</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1643122848522-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1643122848522-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
